==English==
===Noun===
'''lah'''

#(''Music'') An anglicised spelling of [[la#Noun|la]].
#An especially common Singaporean slang that is added to daily talk, to emphasize a point or to simply punctuate a sentence. Usage of this word is more than common in Singapore and is rather the bane of [[Singlish]]. ''Please lah, he's only doing this so he can earn your money'' or ''Don't think so much lah!''